OL,3,CMan hospitalised and two arrested
OL,4,Cafter serious assault outside hotel
OL,6,FA man has been airlifted to a UK
OL,7,Fhospital in a serious condition after
OL,8,Fbeing assaulted outside an Alderney
OL,9,Fhotel.
OL,11,FThe incident happened on Saturday 9
OL,12,FMay, outside The Georgian House on
OL,13,FVictoria Street.
OL,15,FA 46-year-old man has been charged
OL,16,Fwith causing grievous bodily harm with
OL,17,Fintent and was remanded in custody
OL,18,Ffollowing a court appearance on Monday
OL,19,F(11 May).
