OL,3,CMan hospitalised and two arrested
OL,4,Cafter serious assault outside hotel
OL,6,FA 48-year-old man has also been
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of assault and
OL,8,Fis currently in police custody.
OL,10,FDetectives are continuing to carry out
OL,11,Fenquiries and would like to speak to
OL,12,Fanyone with information about what
OL,13,Fhappened.
OL,15,FGuernsey Police can be contacted on
OL,16,F01481 222 222 or anonymously through
OL,17,Fthe independent charity Crimestoppers
OL,18,Fon 0800 555 111.
